186270A3.Line7.121C9F: I hope to see you again when you are next in Zarbinzet. Travel safe, friend.

3FDEC6E1.Line5.121C9F: Before I can return to Zarbinzet, I must perform the final rites for my fellow crusaders that died here. They deserve that at least.

8ED7735D.Line1.121C9F: I was worried we would not find it... But it seems the Light shines even here. Your help shall not be forgotten.

DF0D9F2A.VoiceDir1.121C9F: You've found your master's armor, meaning you can continue her legacy. Emotional. Proud. Powerful.
